cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper deals with instance segmentation in images using natural language descriptions, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed approach uses a deep neural network with recurrent layers, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the experiments are conducted on a dataset of still images, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM).
